Description:
SIMPLY STUNNING EX-DISPLAY HOME!!!
This absolutely stunning Dennis Family ex-display home ticks every single box, located in the popular Livingston Estate, opposite to Casey Race Recreational Facility minutes from Casey Fields. This stunning 29.2 square* home set conveniently on a 512 sqm* block in the heart of Cranbourne East, walking distance to local parklands, Casey Center, bus services, Cranbourne East Secondary College and a short drive to the shopping center. This could be a perfect choice for those looking for a quality family home in a well sought after location.
This incredible home features four spacious bedrooms plus a study, the master bedroom has two separate walk in robes and a huge ensuite with oversized shower, double vanity and separate toilet, whilst all the other bedrooms also has featuring walk in robes.
The kitchen is at the heart of the home and features an enormous waterfall island bench, 900mm oven, built in microwave, dishwasher and large butlers pantry with sink and plenty of cupboard space. The kitchen overlooks the open plan living/dining area which features double sliders that open out to the stunning alfresco with built in BBQ. There is also a completely separate theatre room with double sliding doors. Other features of this fantastic home include ducted heating and cooling, alarm system, led lighting throughout, family bathroom with separate toilet, plenty of storage, double remote garage with internal access and extremely low maintenance gardens.
Be the first ones to inspect and make an offer as this beautiful home will not last long, PLEASE CALL VAS FOR A PRIVATE INSPECTION TODAY.

Description:
FAVOURABLE LOCATION
Beautifully established and cared for boasting multiple stylish living spaces including a theatre room on an easily maintainable 402m2 allotment within the Parks Edge estate.
This home features a separate theatre room with bar/ second living area and a spacious meals/ family area adjoining the light-filled kitchen with ample bench space large pantry stone tops and modern stainless steel appliances.
Master includes a walk in robe with spacious ensuite boasting double shower & vanity while a further three bedrooms have built in robes and are serviced by a stylish central bathroom. Ducted heating for winter warmth and evaporative cooling for your comfort plus the convenience of internal access from the double garage with remote controlled door, will keep the whole family happy.
Summer living is catered for with a decked entertainment BBQ area flowing from the meals area and low maintenance grassed area for the kids to play.
Additional features
Downlights and feature lighting
Gas boosted solar hot water system
Grey water system
Large decked area
Separate laundry
Bar area to the theatre room
Upgraded façade
Set in the Parks Edge estate in Cranbourne East this property is close to Shops, schools, freeways and all that the Casey area has to offer. At this price this property won't last long so book your inspection now

Description:
ENTERTAINERS DELIGHT!
Located in the Cascades on Clyde estate sits an exceptional example of family living in an estate that is second to none.
Upon entry you will be immediately impressed, with a keen eye for detail this home has spared no expense. Four bedrooms plus study, the generous sized master comes complete with a big walk in robe, full en-suite that includes dual vanities and an extended shower space.
The hostess kitchen is a chef's dream and is complete with quality stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher, 900mm range hood, 5-burner gas cook top, caesar stone bench tops, glass splash back, ample overhead storage and bench space plus a walk in pantry. All of this overlooking your separate meals and rear living zone.
Not only is this home fitted out with top quality fixtures and fittings it also presents a grand capacity to accommodate even the largest of families, this is truly an entertainers delight with multiple living zones on offer!
Additional extras include: ducted heating & evaporative cooling, down lights throughout, neutral tones, alfresco & extended pergola plus much more!
The additions don't stop there, step through the sliding doors and enjoy your well-appointed alfresco area and extended pergola with decking! This provides the perfect setting to sit back and relax after the long working week or to entertain friends and family!
Surrounded by top end properties and is within walking distance to picturesque wetlands, this home boasts convenience. Other estate features include Class- A recycled water ensuring lush gardens year round, over 14 hectares of parkland and public open space, public BBQ facilities, playgrounds and walking tracks.
Those who are business savvy will appreciate this Telstra smart community positioned within a short drive to all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne. Minutes away from freeway access en route to the Melbourne CBD, the popular Clyde Primary School, Casey Fields football ground/Casey Race aquatic centre and the Town Centre. Not to mention just minutes away from the Selandra Rise and Hunt Club village shopping centres.
From front to back this home was completed with an exceptional eye for detail and will be the perfect residence for those that expect nothing but the best!
BOOK AN INSPECTION TODAY, IT MAY BE GONE TOMORROW! - *PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS*

Description:
Young, modern & desirable location
CRANBOURNE EAST - LIVINGSTON ESTATE: You can't help but feel at home once you step through this beautiful welcoming home built by Boutique Homes. Positioned in the popular Livingston Estate with neatly presented homes and across the road from a park, this home will suit any family, first home buyer or someone downsizing.
Offering a highly functional floor plan with a welcoming entrance leading you to the master bedroom with walk-in robe and full twin sink ensuite. The other 3 bedrooms have sliding robes.
The kitchen has a window splashback and offers stainless steel appliances - 900mm gas stove, electric oven, range hood, dishwasher and built in microwave. Caesar stone bench tops with an island bench overlooking the family/meals area. The kitchen has ample storage with overhead cupboards.
Outside you have a large grass area and an al fresco area for year round enjoyment. The blend of indoor outdoor living is the feature of this home with light and bright living areas.
Some of the extras of this home includes:
- Colour bond fencing
- Ceasar stone in bathrooms
- Floating timber floorboards
- Built in microwave
- Ducted heating
- Evaporative cooling
- Window splashback
- Day night blinds
- Alarm System
- Low Maintenance Gardens
The location of this quality home is second to none with the park on your door step your family can enjoy the open space for many years to come.
Cranbourne East is located on the outskirts of Cranbourne Central. The area offers Cranbourne East Primary and Cranbourne East Secondary College as well as Cranbourne Secondary College and is surrounded by multiple Shopping Centres. Also located nearby is the newly constructed Casey Fields football ground, Casey Race Recreation & Aquatic Centre, and Casey Library.

Family Living with a Pool
Set in the sought-after Avenues Estate, and in close proximity to Casey Race, Casey Fields, shops, public transport and schools is this absolute hidden gem of a home. Set on a large 620sqm (approx.) corner block and boasting 3 bedrooms, plus study, 3 living areas, plus a solar heated swimming pool, this home will leave you wanting for nothing.

Accommodation needs are met with a spacious master suite with walk-in robe and ensuite, remaining 2 bedrooms are serviced by a bright and spacious family bathroom including corner spa bath. Outside is a solar-heated salt pool, with paved entertaining area and pergola, surrounded by landscaped gardens and garden shed.

Description:
Modern Style in Cascades on Clyde. OPEN CANCELLED 22ND DECEMBER
Directly adjacent the vast reserve in the heart of Cascades on Clyde, this elegant modern design, coupled with all the creature comforts make this three bedroom plus study home a very enticing package for starters, downsizers or investors.
Beautifully sized for comfortable family living, with two spacious living areas skirting a sleek contemporary kitchen with beech-look cabinetry, breakfast bar, dishwasher and gas cooktop. Beyond sliding glass doors the covered alfresco patio rolls onto a fully fenced lawn ideal for kids and pets to play on this 453m2 (approx) allotment.
Well considered family zoning places a lovely master bedroom with walk-in robe and ensuite beside the formal lounge and study, cocooning children in a separate wing in the rear of the home with easy access to the second bathroom.
Just 10 years old and nicely maintained, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, a garden shed and double remote garage with internal access and rear rollerdoor provide all the coveted extras, while tiled floors, waffle carpeting and a fresh neutral palette offer a blank canvas to infuse your own style and decor.
An easy stroll to the Selanda Rise Shopping Centre, public transport and the picturesque wetlands walking trails, with a selection of excellent schools beyond, the property is less than an hour to Melbourne CBD with easy freeway access.

Description:
Quality Home with Two Living Areas
This outstanding 2,700mm high ceiling home has been built and finished to the highest of standards. Boasting four bedrooms, two living areas plus a study nook. Master bedroom has an ensuite with a spacious walk in robe, remaining bedrooms will accommodate double beds and have built in robes. Main bathroom with extended shower base and ducted heating as well as a separate toilet. Spacious open plan stunning kitchen with stainless steel appliances including a 900mm built in oven and a 5-gas burner cooktop, dishwasher, stone benches, a walk-in pantry and a good size linen overlooking the natural light filled meals and family area. Offering all the comforts with ducted heating, carpets in all bedrooms and in one living area, remote control double garage with handy internal access. This beautiful family home is perfect opportunity for the first home owner or astute investor. Be quick to act, quality homes like this don't last!

Description:
True Hunt Club Opportunity!
CRANBOURNE EAST: If you are looking to buy a great family home in a great location then 84 Scotsdale Drive needs to be seen to be appreciated!
With a functional, free flowing floor plan the property itself features 3 generous bedrooms and study. The master bedroom offers a WIR and a FES, the balance of the bedrooms all have BIR and nearby to the family bathroom with separate bath and shower facilities.
The hostess kitchen is the central hub of the home and is finished with a good amount of cupboard space, large bench space, tiled splash back, S/S appliances including oven, gas cook top, rangehood and dishwasher.
Take advantage of the 2 separate living zones making year-round formal and informal entertaining a breeze! Relax with a good movie or a book with the front living area, carefree day to day living will be enjoyed in the family zone or grab a seat around the kitchen table with the family in the dining area.
Added internal extras are gas ducted heating, s/s cooling, a mix of tiles and carpet and neutral tones throughout.
Step outside and be greeted by a sensational street scape offering a modern facade and landscaping. A wide lengthy concrete driveway leads to the remote double garage with rear access suitable for exrtra car, boats and trailers. The backyard is perfect for the entire family and pets, with room to build the perfect pergola area to your liking (STCA).
The Hunt Club is a multi award winning estate offering numerous parks, wetlands, walking and bicycle paths as well as a complete range of childcare, primary (Cranbourne East Primary) and secondary schools (Cranbourne East Secondary College). Buses weave through the estate making the newly built shopping centre complete with Woolworths & Aldi easily accessible. Recycled water, high speed broadband and environmentally friendly designs are all part of the estate.
Don't waste your time with a frustrating building process! It's all here waiting for you and you don't even need to lift a finger!

Description:
Great for family
In the Livingston Estate this modern home offers an exceptional life style with generous spaces and is defined by its openness and abundance of natural light boasting
- Four robed bedrooms two bathroom and double lock up garage
- A serene color scheme sets a restful mood in this master bedroom with walk in robe and ensuite
- The other three bedrooms all with built in robes
- With quality carpeting and neutral wall tones this space is a constellation of star elements
- The formal living and open plan living area offers ideal setting for relaxing and entertaining
- A continuous living-dining-kitchen space with stainless steel appliances, dishwasher and stays clutter-free thanks to plentiful drawers and cabinets
- Sparkling family bathroom, separate toilet and laundry
- Ducted heating and split cooling for year round comfort
- Outdoor Alfresco with low maintenance garden
Proudly placed only a stone's throw from parkland, Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre, Cranbourne train station, buses, plus Cranbourne Royal Botanic Gardens, close to Lighthouse Christian College and Cranbourne Primary.
